description: Product Description Mama Bear Disney - Ultra Sensitive - (12x60). These ultra-sensitive wipes are as kind to the planet as they are to your baby’s skin. Made from 99% water, they’re free from perfume, which makes them the perfect choice for no-fuss, gentle cleansing. Ingredients INGREDIENTS: Aqua, Sodium Gluconate, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid, Myristamidopropyl PG-Dimonium Chloride Phosphate, Sodium Citrate. Directions Remove the wipe from its packaging. Gently wipe over face, hands or body until clean. Discard the used wipe. Close the lid of the container after use to prevent drying out of the remaining wipes. Safety Warning Do not use near eyes. Discontinue use if skin irritation occurs. Dispose of used wipes appropriately; do not dispose in the toilet. Box Contains Each box contains 12 packs, with 60 wipes in each pack (720 wipes in total).
